(8048, 261, 'sections_0_layout_0_content', 'What: Orr Wedding\r\nWhen: Saturday, September 8, 2018. Ceremony begins at 6:00 PM\r\nWhere: Edgewood Tahoe (100 LAKE PARKWAY LAKE TAHOE, NV 89449)\r\n\r\nFriends and Family,\r\nWelcome to the Orr Wedding website! Here you will find any information you will need regarding our wedding celebration.\r\nOur wedding will take place in the beautiful South Lake Tahoe, Nevada. We both shared a love for Lake Tahoe before we met, and that love deepened when we it visited together for the first time as a couple. Between the stunning blue waters, pine trees and nature all around, we knew there was no better place on earth to host our special day. So mark your calendars on September 8, 2018 so that we can celebrate with you all!\r\nPlease check out the details within this site to help with all your planning needs.\r\n\"We\'re all a little weird, and life\'s a little weird. And when we find someone whose weirdness is compatible with ours, we join up with them and fall in mutual weirdness and call it love.\" – Dr. Seuss\r\n'),
