(8234, 269, 'sections_0_layout_2_content', 'Accommodations:\r\nGuests are more than welcome to stay at the Edgewood Resort. Unfortunately room accommodations for weddings are not offered. Here are a few other of our favorite hotels in the South Lake Tahoe area: \r\nEdgewood Tahoe (our hotel): http://www.edgewoodtahoe.com/\r\nThe Landing Resort: http://thelandingtahoe.com/\r\nMontbleu: https://www.montbleuresort.com/\r\nHarrahs: https://www.caesars.com/harrahs-tahoe?utm_campaign=GMB&utm_source=google&utm_medium=local&utm_term=HarrahsLakeTahoe&utm_content=hotel\r\nHard Rock Hotel & Casino: https://hardrockcasinolaketahoe.com/\r\nRenting a cabin may be a great option as well! \r\n\r\nPlease also note the following:\r\nBe aware of heavy traffic/road closures if residing outside of South Lake Tahoe. \r\nThe nearest airport is Reno, Nevada. South Lake Tahoe is an hour drive away. \r\nIf flying, renting a car is recommended as Uber/Lyfts are limited.\r\nThe hotel provides a shuttle service after the wedding for easy transportation back to the main street, but Uber/Lyft should also be accessible. \r\n\r\nThings to see:\r\nEmerald Bay State Park\r\nhttps://travel.usnews.com/Lake_Tahoe_CA/Things_To_Do/Emerald_Bay_State_Park_62084/\r\nChimney Beach\r\nhttps://www.alltrails.com/trail/us/nevada/chimney-beach-trail\r\nMount Tallac Loop:\r\nhttps://www.yelp.com/biz/mount-tallac-loop-south-lake-tahoe\r\nTahoe Rim Trail:\r\nhttps://tahoerimtrail.org/\r\nPlaces to eat:\r\nWest Shore Café\r\nhttps://www.westshorecafe.com/\r\nGarwoods – Try the Wet Woody!\r\nhttps://www.garwoods.com/\r\nBasecamp Pizza:\r\nhttps://basecamppizzaco.com/\r\n\r\nRehearsal dinner for the day-before (9/7/2018) *wedding party only:\r\n12:00 – 2:00pm at the Riva Grill\r\nTimeline for the day-of the event (9/8/2018): \r\n \r\n6:00 - 6:45pm Ceremony\r\n6:45 - 7:45pm Cocktail Hour\r\n7:45 - 8:45pm Dinner Service\r\n8:45 - 11:45pm Toasts/Dancing/Reception\r\n11:45pm Reception Ends \r\n\r\n\r\nWedding hashtag: #ForevOrrInLove\r\n'),
