(8270, 270, 'sections_0_layout_1_content', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\"We\'re all a little weird, and life\'s a little weird. And when we find someone whose weirdness is compatible with ours, we join up with them and fall in mutual weirdness and call it love.\"<br /> – Dr. Seuss</em></p>'),
