(8324, 272, 'sections_0_layout_2_content', '<p>Guests are more than welcome to stay at the Edgewood Resort. Unfortunately room accommodations for weddings are not offered.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>Accommodations:</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><a href=\"http://www.edgewoodtahoe.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Edgewood Tahoe</a> (our hotel)</li>\r\n  <li><a href=\"http://thelandingtahoe.com/\" target=\"_blank\">The Landing Resort</a></li>\r\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.montbleuresort.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Montbleu</a></li>\r\n  <li><a href=\"https://tahoesouth.com/stay/harrahs-lake-tahoe/\" target=\"_blank\">Harrahs</a></li>\r\n  <li><a href=\"https://hardrockcasinolaketahoe.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Hard Rock Hotel & Casino</a></li>\r\n  <li>Renting a cabin may be a great option as well!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h5>Please also note the following:</h5>\r\n<p>Be aware of heavy traffic/road closures if residing outside of South Lake Tahoe. The nearest airport is Reno, Nevada. South Lake Tahoe is an hour drive away. If flying, renting a car is recommended as Uber/Lyfts are limited. The hotel provides a shuttle service after the wedding for easy transportation back to the main street, but Uber/Lyft should also be accessible.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>Things to see:</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.parks.ca.gov/?page_id=506\" target=\"_blank\">Emerald Bay State Park</a></li>\r\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.alltrails.com/trail/us/nevada/chimney-beach-trail\" target=\"_blank\">Chimney Beach</a></li>\r\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.alltrails.com/trail/us/california/mt-tallac-trail\" target=\"_blank\">Mount Tallac Loop</a></li>\r\n  <li><a href=\"https://tahoerimtrail.org/maps-trail-info/\" target=\"_blank\">Tahoe Rim Trail</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h5>Places to eat:</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.westshorecafe.com/\" target=\"_blank\">West Shore Café</a></li>\r\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.garwoods.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Garwoods</a> – Try the Wet Woody!</li>\r\n  <li><a href=\"https://basecamppizzaco.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Basecamp Pizza</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h5>Wedding chedule:</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Rehearsal dinner for the day-before (9/7/2018) <sup>* wedding party only</sup>: 12:00 – 2:00pm at the <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/vHFKgKQtm8K2\" target=\"_blank\">Riva Grill</a></li>\r\n  <li>\r\n    Wedding day (9/8/2018):\r\n    <ul>\r\n      <li>6:00 - 6:45pm Ceremony</li>\r\n      <li>6:45 - 7:45pm Cocktail Hour</li>\r\n      <li>7:45 - 8:45pm Dinner Service</li>\r\n      <li>8:45 - 11:45pm Toasts/Dancing/Reception</li>\r\n      <li>11:45pm Reception Ends</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n  </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Wedding hashtag: <span class=\"bold\">#ForevOrrInLove</span></h3>'),
