(8452, 275, 'sections_2_layout_0_content', 'Guests are more than welcome to stay at the Edgewood Resort. Unfortunately room accommodations for weddings are not offered.\r\n<h5>Accommodations:</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.edgewoodtahoe.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Edgewood Tahoe</a> (our hotel)</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://thelandingtahoe.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Landing Resort</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.montbleuresort.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Montbleu</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://tahoesouth.com/stay/harrahs-lake-tahoe/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Harrahs</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://hardrockcasinolaketahoe.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hard Rock Hotel &amp; Casino</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Renting a cabin may be a great option as well!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Please also note the following:</h5>\r\nBe aware of heavy traffic/road closures if residing outside of South Lake Tahoe. The nearest airport is Reno, Nevada. South Lake Tahoe is an hour drive away. If flying, renting a car is recommended as Uber/Lyfts are limited. The hotel provides a shuttle service after the wedding for easy transportation back to the main street, but Uber/Lyft should also be accessible.\r\n<h5>Things to see:</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.parks.ca.gov/?page_id=506\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Emerald Bay State Park</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.alltrails.com/trail/us/nevada/chimney-beach-trail\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Chimney Beach</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.alltrails.com/trail/us/california/mt-tallac-trail\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mount Tallac Loop</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://tahoerimtrail.org/maps-trail-info/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tahoe Rim Trail</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Places to eat:</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.westshorecafe.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">West Shore Café</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.garwoods.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Garwoods</a> – Try the Wet Woody!</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://basecamppizzaco.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Basecamp Pizza</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Wedding schedule:</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Rehearsal dinner for the day-before (9/7/2018) <sup>* wedding party only</sup>: 12:00 – 2:00pm at the <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/vHFKgKQtm8K2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Riva Grill</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Wedding day (9/8/2018):\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>6:00 - 6:45pm Ceremony</li>\r\n 	<li>6:45 - 7:45pm Cocktail Hour</li>\r\n 	<li>7:45 - 8:45pm Dinner Service</li>\r\n 	<li>8:45 - 11:45pm Toasts/Dancing/Reception</li>\r\n 	<li>11:45pm Reception Ends</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Wedding hashtag: <span class=\"bold\">#ForevOrrInLove</span></h3>'),
